00:53:47,650 --> 00:53:49,950
<font color="yellow">What else is this, then?</font>

674
00:53:50,820 --> 00:53:54,680
<font color="yellow">I can never take my eyes off of you.</font>

675
00:53:54,680 --> 00:53:58,150
<font color="yellow">It's not what you think. I really need to burn this.</font>

676
00:53:58,150 --> 00:54:00,550
<font color="yellow">You could have just torn it apart instead.</font>

677
00:54:00,550 --> 00:54:02,650
<font color="yellow">Is it a secret document? Gosh, it's hot.</font>

678
00:54:02,650 --> 00:54:04,780
<font color="yellow">I'll clean it up.</font>

679
00:54:06,250 --> 00:54:08,620
<font color="yellow">I can't trust you with anything.</font>

