682
00:54:27,080 --> 00:54:28,420
<font color="yellow">Then...</font>

683
00:54:30,580 --> 00:54:32,120
<font color="yellow">Then what?</font>

684
00:54:33,250 --> 00:54:35,320
<font color="yellow">I can't find anyone trustworthy to put in charge,</font>

685
00:54:35,420 --> 00:54:37,880
<font color="yellow">so I just can't leave Korea.</font>

686
00:54:38,750 --> 00:54:41,580
<font color="yellow">You'll make it a haunted house in less than a year.</font>

687
00:54:49,680 --> 00:54:50,680
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

688
00:55:18,420 --> 00:55:19,420
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

689
00:55:20,520 --> 00:55:22,780
<font color="yellow">I'm not educated properly...</font>

690
00:55:24,120 --> 00:55:26,580
<font color="yellow">and I'm practically a beggar with no savings.</font>

691
00:55:26,750 --> 00:55:28,220
<font color="yellow">What a fool.</font>

692
00:55:29,120 --> 00:55:30,480
<font color="yellow">I know I'm a fool.</font>

