00:55:31,550 --> 00:55:33,980
<font color="yellow">I'm a con artist with a record.</font>

694
00:55:34,850 --> 00:55:36,420
<font color="yellow">Don't you get it?</font>

695
00:55:37,950 --> 00:55:40,650
<font color="yellow">It's not often, but you do shine.</font>

696
00:55:42,920 --> 00:55:43,980
<font color="yellow">When?</font>

697
00:55:46,320 --> 00:55:47,620
<font color="yellow">As Geum Bi's dad.</font>

698
00:56:08,120 --> 00:56:10,780
<font color="yellow">(Dear Ms. Go Kang Hee)</font>

699
00:56:11,520 --> 00:56:14,820
<font color="yellow">After her death, all of Yang Yoon Ok's assets...</font>

