705
00:56:30,250 --> 00:56:33,520
<font color="yellow">she heard she had a granddaughter and changed her will.</font>

706
00:56:37,320 --> 00:56:38,750
<font color="yellow">Before the amendment,</font>

707
00:56:39,550 --> 00:56:41,380
<font color="yellow">was everything left to me?</font>

708
00:56:41,820 --> 00:56:45,120
<font color="yellow">No, she'd planned to give back to society...</font>

709
00:56:45,120 --> 00:56:46,680
<font color="yellow">by donating to a few charities.</font>

710
00:56:48,620 --> 00:56:50,020
<font color="yellow">She didn't even have much.</font>

711
00:56:52,820 --> 00:56:54,880
<font color="yellow">How much are her assets worth?</font>

712
00:56:58,650 --> 00:57:01,420
<font color="yellow">Including her savings and securities,</font>

713
00:57:02,620 --> 00:57:04,020
<font color="yellow">about 1.5 million dollars.</font>

714
00:57:06,620 --> 00:57:10,380
<font color="yellow">Like I said, without the legal guardian's consent,</font>

715
00:57:10,880 --> 00:57:15,320
<font color="yellow">the assets cannot be sold or transferred at all.</font>

716
00:57:16,350 --> 00:57:18,920
<font color="yellow">Who is her legal guardian?</font>

717
00:57:24,080 --> 00:57:25,120
<font color="yellow">It's me.</font>

718
00:57:35,920 --> 00:57:38,280
<font color="yellow">How can I make you consent?</font>

719
00:57:38,880 --> 00:57:40,880
<font color="yellow">I won't consent.</font>

720
00:58:12,050 --> 00:58:14,480
<font color="yellow">(Yoo Geum Bi)</font>

721
00:58:55,150 --> 00:58:57,980
<font color="yellow">(My Fair Lady 2016)</font>

722
00:58:58,250 --> 00:58:59,980
<font color="yellow">What is she to you?</font>

723
00:58:59,980 --> 00:59:01,880
<font color="yellow">I have a good reason to borrow it.</font>

724
00:59:01,880 --> 00:59:04,350
