725
00:59:04,350 --> 00:59:06,220
<font color="yellow">her medicine will cost over 1,000 dollars a month.</font>

726
00:59:06,480 --> 00:59:08,280
<font color="yellow">Are you sure it's 1.5 million?</font>

727
00:59:08,450 --> 00:59:11,150
<font color="yellow">She left her assets to Yoo Geum Bi, not you.</font>

728
00:59:11,150 --> 00:59:12,680
<font color="yellow">How dare you come here?</font>

729
00:59:12,680 --> 00:59:14,320
<font color="yellow">Does a mom need a reason to see her own child?</font>

