00:59:23,980 --> 00:59:25,020
<font color="yellow">You can't do that.</font>

738
00:59:25,020 --> 00:59:27,220
<font color="yellow">She won't recognize her if she gets older.</font>

739
00:59:27,220 --> 00:59:30,020
<font color="yellow">If she dies before seeing her mom,</font>

